---
import AxonLogo from '../AxonLogo.astro';
---

<section class="section section--cream about-developer">
  <div class="section-inner" style="text-align: center;">
    <div class="about-developer__logo">
      <AxonLogo width={160} />
    </div>
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">About the Developer</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">About Axon Developers</h2>
    <p class="section-body reveal reveal-delay-1">
      Axon Developers stands at the cutting edge of global living
      experiences. We believe living spaces are defined not just by their
      structures, but by the people who move into them — so our endeavour
      goes beyond aesthetics and design to encourage smart, long-term
      decisions. Through Integrated Tourism Townships in the most thoroughly
      vetted locations in the country — like The Riviera in Vagade,
      Sindhudurg — Axon Developers is creating an entirely new way of
      riverside living.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-developer__logo {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
